Reasoning: The paper deals with learning the inverse dynamics of robot manipulators using Gaussian processes, which is a topic in robotics (cs.RO). The use of Gaussian processes for learning also falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of the learned model for feed-forward control, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper proposes a novel cascaded approach for Gaussian process learning, which falls under the category of neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE).
